    "description": "EarthSciData.jl NEI2016Monthly loader expressed in the STAC-like DataLoader schema. Corresponds to EarthSciData.jl src/nei2016monthly.jl — struct NEI2016MonthlyEmisFileSet (lines 142-166) with relpath (lines 173-177) and the sector-based {sector} substitution. The runtime-side diurnal and day-of-week scale factors (DIURNAL_FACTORS, DayofWeekFactors_* and the @register_symbolic functions at lines 4-133) are runtime behavior and intentionally not in the schema — they are applied during rate-expression evaluation. All emissions are only available for 2016 and are gridded on the 12US1 Lambert Conformal grid.",
